{"tid":1711714,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陶傑 : 是不是整座大學，變成了林鄭月娥眼中的暴亂基地？","createTime":"2019-11-12T12:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T12:29:07.000Z","uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20584842ac85b969071adaddf4b184d345010220","tid":1711714,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"中文大學變成了一座烽火台。<br />\n<br />\n是不是整座大學，變成了林鄭月娥眼中的暴亂基地？<br />\n<br />\n三百年前，雍正皇帝也派清兵攻打並火燒少林寺，因為少林寺被認定窩藏叛亂的反清志士。<br />\n<br />\n當年英國殖民地政府，見民國知識分子錢穆等人，逃亡香港，保存宣揚在大陸成為灰燼的中國儒家文化，於心不忍，將這一角山水，建設成中文大學。<br />\n<br />\n今日，香港和海外的中大校友，不知作何感想？<br />\n<br />\n中國人的歷史悲劇，在這籠黑煙之中，見盡其宿命循環。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/75557378_3172138489525319_5664321144774197248_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQkm1_yB4Vq3h47B6OjwOQMf9CadlOoQxdCcqzaHyTc2qF1AMfkz4Yn6ukHuh6ufrZI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=77ae4d9c00b19ecbe97fe75c09f97931&amp;oe=5E4ABB13\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F75557378_3172138489525319_5664321144774197248_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQkm1_yB4Vq3h47B6OjwOQMf9CadlOoQxdCcqzaHyTc2qF1AMfkz4Yn6ukHuh6ufrZI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D77ae4d9c00b19ecbe97fe75c09f97931%26oe%3D5E4ABB13&h=62bc59fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e10affcee7a4424c28bf2e9d5893102fced36b8e","tid":1711714,"uid":300785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:29:07.000Z","msg":"咁狗屋咪喺犯案現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}